{"name": "naga-helper", "metadata": {"name": "naga-helper", "version": "0.2.10", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/sjn4048/naga_helper", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Analyze reports of riichi mahjong AI NAGA and Mortal.", "upload_time": 1733211247}, "documentation": ["# NAGA/Mortal\u724c\u8c31\u89e3\u6790\r\n\r\n\u8fd9\u662f [NAGA\u52a9\u624b](https://ricochet.cn/riichi/naga) \u7f51\u7ad9NAGA/Mortal\u724c\u8c31\u89e3\u6790\u7684\u4ee3\u7801\u3002\r\n\r\n\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u5f00\u6e90\u8fd9\u90e8\u5206\u4ee3\u7801\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5176\u6280\u672f\u542b\u91d1\u91cf\u6700\u9ad8\uff08\u6709\u5b9e\u9645\u4ef7\u503c\uff09\u3001\u8ba1\u7b97\u91cf\u8f83\u91cd\uff08\u7f13\u89e3\u7f51\u7ad9\u8d1f\u8f7d\uff09\u3001\u4e14\u6b22\u8fce\u5404\u4f4d\u8d21\u732e\u3002\u7f51\u7ad9\u5176\u4f59\u90e8\u5206\u4e3b\u8981\u662f\u91cdCRUD\u903b\u8f91\uff0c\u53c2\u8003\u4ef7\u503c\u4e0d\u5927\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u505a\u5f00\u6e90\u3002\r\n\r\n## Install\r\n```shell\r\npip install naga_helper\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \u6a21\u5757\r\n### analyzer\r\n\u5206\u6790\u73b0\u6709NAGA\u724c\u8c31\u62a5\u544a\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u5f0f\u5982\u4e0b\uff1a\r\n\r\n\u5bfc\u5165pip\u5305\uff1a\r\n```python\r\nfrom naga_helper.analyzer import parse_report\r\nparse_report('NAGA html content')\r\n```\r\n\r\n\u547d\u4ee4\u884c\uff1a\r\n```shell\r\npython naga_helper/analyzer.py <naga\u724c\u8c31\u7f51\u5740> <Mortal\u724c\u8c31id>\r\n```\r\n\u5176\u4e2dMortal\u724c\u8c31id\u4e3a\u9009\u586b\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u586b\u5199\uff0c\u5219\u4f1a\u628aMortal\u7684\u5207\u724c\u9009\u62e9\u5408\u5e76\u5165NAGA\u724c\u8c31\u62a5\u544a\u3002\u6076\u624b\u7387/\u4e00\u81f4\u7387/Rating\u7684\u8ba1\u7b97\u65b9\u5f0f\u4e0eNAGA\u4e00\u81f4\u3002\r\n\r\nnaga\u724c\u8c31\u5730\u5740\u53ef\u4ee5\u540c\u65f6\u7701\u7565\u524d\u7f00\u4e0e\u540e\u7f00\uff0c\u53ea\u4fdd\u7559html key\u3002\r\n\r\n\u683c\u5f0f\u53c2\u8003\uff1a\r\n```shell\r\npython naga_helper/analyzer.py https://naga.dmv.nico/htmls/9a852e2e3a273e1d5a362d69618000684340d3e0e96024e6fa07858afa1afa00v2_2.html 01f7faef6dc7fe5e\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n### plugins\r\n\u5404\u7c7b\u63d2\u4ef6\uff0c\u5305\u62ecNAGA\u7f51\u9875\u6a21\u5757\u7b49\r\n\r\n## \u529f\u80fd\r\n1. NAGA\u724c\u8c31\u62a5\u544a\u5206\u6790\r\n2. Mortal\u724c\u8c31\u62a5\u544a\u5206\u6790 & \u628aMortal\u62a5\u544a\u878d\u5408\u5165NAGA\u754c\u9762\r\n3. NAGA\u7f51\u9875\u7aef\u5feb\u6377\u952e\u6ce8\u5165\u811a\u672c\r\n\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "naga_helper", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "naga_helper.plugins.naga_webpage", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "naga_helper.plugins.naga_webpage.keyboard_shortcut", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "naga_helper.plugins", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "naga_helper.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "naga_helper.utils.get_leaf_path_by_name", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "naga_helper.utils.DotDict", "bases": ["dict"], "methods": [{"name": "naga_helper.utils.DotDict.__getattr__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "k", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns